{"tid":1401912,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［不服來辯］屌撚曬你地班人","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T15:30:06.000Z","uid":120250,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fe6e3aa6acafead1da197f22fc9f2ba588b05f13","tid":1401912,"uid":120250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:20:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化 不割席</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地要做既唔係屌黎屌去，中曬佔中分化計。<br />\n<br />\n我地要多謝前線為我地既付出，多謝身邊所有既手足居民遍地開花。<br />\n<br />\n企前線唔走唔代表無腦，佢地為我地製造左好多文宣食糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n淆底驚死既你，唔該大力推文宣，唔好浪費時間屌鬼，我屌撚曬你班1毛，縮返入老母個閪到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f088abaaa72e8bdc46a49053601a13199ebb490","tid":1401912,"uid":120250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:21:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化 不割席</span></span>"},{"pid":"5841b5c88bf7262e961af38161fc207a0206546b","tid":1401912,"uid":120250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:22:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化 不割席</span></span>"},{"pid":"2ee3df242e02703c54bfeb6d900bcfb69acc2b3a","tid":1401912,"uid":120250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:22:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化 不割席</span></span>"},{"pid":"ae45b2314fdbd7a2f52d84fbea372f4356890f3c","tid":1401912,"uid":120250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:22:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化 不割席</span></span>"},{"pid":"4aded646308b8ca677000f8688c5bab8940d2925","tid":1401912,"uid":120250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:22:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"col